reviews.text: Good place to eat economical, with Healthy option

This Yunnan noodle specialist is best of the best in HK. A must try when U are in HK. They have many outlets all over HK and even inside the Hong Kong International Airport at terminal 2. 
Besides their delicious spicy and non spicy noodles,they also have various traditonal chinese side dishes too.
cheap local mix ian with high cp value
the food is cheap and delicious

Most consistent rice noodle place you can find in Hong Kong. This is the "Starbucks" of noodle shops. Probably not the best, but definitely not bad on any day, any branch. The only downside is the cost can rack up surprisingly fast as you order side dishes and the wings

result.name: 譚仔三哥米線

reviews.text: 大衆化食物。地方亦算整潔，價錢不貴，可食飽肚。
中午唔好去，被安排7個男人一張檯，手撞手頭撞頭，口水傳口水。
抵食夾大份，配料種類繁多，除米線外還有多欵美味小食。

只有3哥先有素食選擇。

豆卜金菇生菜，素茄湯+2蚊，尖椒皮蛋，凍檸茶，共76蚊。

雖然素茄湯多人order，但唔合本人口味，下次要試酸辣素湯，如果都係唔ok，要轉回普通素湯。
東西不錯，地方也ok，亦算清潔。
